These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, turtle, mouse, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, rugby, tennis
1. the owner of the mouse is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is rowing##2
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
4. the person who's sport is rowing is not the owner of the mouse##6
5. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
6. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Pet   | lizard  | frog | mouse | turtle  |
| Sport   | biathlon | rugby   | tennis  | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, goldfish, guinea-pig
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, journalist, nurse, project-manager
1. the project-manager is not to the left of the project-manager##8
2. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
3. the owner of the dog is the journalist##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the hedgehog##2
5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the owner of the goldfish and the designer##7
6. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
7. the designer is not to the left of the designer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Pet   | goldfish | hedgehog          | guinea-pig | dog     |
| Job    | nurse      | project-manager | designer | journalist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, electrician, nurse, paramedic
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, italian, colombian, brazilian
1. the spanish is not to the left of the nurse##8
2. the italian is on the far left##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the bartender##1
4. the electrician is in an even position##4
5. the paramedic is on the far left or far right##3
6. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
7. the paramedic is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | bartender | electrician | nurse     | paramedic |
| Nationality   | italian    | brazilian   | spanish | colombian    |

