.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, comedy, family, romance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the person watching romance movies is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
5. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | comedy         | romance   | time-travel    |
| Sport         | parkour | weightlifting | soccer | lacrosse |

