.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, electronic, dubstep, punk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, handball, rugby
1. the fan of punk is somewhere between the fan of funk and the fan of electronic##7
2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
3. the fan of punk is somewhere between the fan of dubstep and the fan of funk##7
4. the fan of dubstep is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the fan of electronic and the person who's sport is cycling##7
6. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the fan of punk##5
7. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the fan of funk##8
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | dubstep | punk | funk    |
| Sport         | climbing | rugby   | handball   | cycling |

