.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
House: ranch-style, farmhouse, craftsman, art-deco
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, indie, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
3. the craftsman house is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
5. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the left of the farmhouse house##5
6. the art-deco house is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
7. the art-deco house is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| House          | art-deco | ranch-style | farmhouse  | craftsman |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | pop         | indie | ambient |

