.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, dressmaker, entrepreneur, project-manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, epic, documentary
1. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the person watching documentary movies##8
2. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5
3. the dressmaker is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person watching epic movies is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the dressmaker##7
5. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the project-manager##8
6. the project-manager is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the entrepreneur##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Job     | dressmaker | entrepreneur | project-manager | doctor     |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | epic        | documentary          | disaster |

