.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, indie, pop
House: futuristic, victorian, craftsman, farmhouse
1. the fan of classical is between the fan of pop and the futuristic house##2
2. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
4. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
5. the victorian house is the victorian house##1
6. the fan of indie is not the craftsman house##6
7. the fan of pop is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
8. the futuristic house is not to the left of the victorian house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | classical | indie | dubstep |
| House     | farmhouse | victorian       | futuristic  | craftsman    |

