.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-10::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, rowing, soccer, snowboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, snowmobile, taxi
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the snowmobile##2
2. the person driving the airplane is not the person who's sport is rowing##6
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8
5. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Sport         | soccer | skiing      | snowboarding   | rowing  |
| Transport   | taxi    | motorbike | airplane | snowmobile |

