2. the indian is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
3. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
4. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the japanese##8
5. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the indian##8
6. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| Nationality   | dutch     | japanese | indian | german |
| Pet     | ferret | rat  | chinchilla    | goat   |

