.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, juice, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, hip-hop, blues, pop
1. the fan of pop is not to the right of the fan of techno##8
2. the fan of pop is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the fan of techno is somewhere between the fan of blues and the person drinking fanta##7
7. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | fanta         | juice    | cola       |
| Music-Genre      | hip-hop | pop | techno | blues |

