.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, sprite, tea
4 different games are played: chess, whist, monopoly, scrabble
1. the person playing scrabble is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
2. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking tea and the person playing monopoly##2
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
6. the person playing chess is between the person playing whist and the person playing scrabble##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage   | 7up     | almond-milk | tea        | sprite       |
| Game      | monopoly | whist  | chess | scrabble |

