.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, tennis, handball, biathlon
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, drawing, reading, video-games
1. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
7. the person who's sport is handball is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Sport    | biathlon        | tennis | soccer | handball |
| Hobby   | video-games | reading | drawing   | camping    |

