.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hamster, hedgehog
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, spanish, mexican, egyptian
1. the spanish is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
2. the mexican is on the right of the egyptian##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the egyptian##8
4. the owner of the hamster is the colombian##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the spanish and the colombian##7
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the mexican is between the egyptian and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | frog    | hedgehog | chinchilla | hamster |
| Nationality   | spanish | egyptian      | mexican     | colombian     |

 